productName: Orgain Organic Plant Based Protein Almond Milk, Unsweetened, Soy Free
details: At Orgain we don’t do “watered down.” Our Organic Protein Almondmilk - Unsweetened Vanilla - is rich, creamy, and delicious. Enjoy our unsweetened organic almond milk anyway you like - in coffee, cereal, baking and cooking, or straight out of a glass! Go ahead - give it a try, and feel the difference of an almond-based milk that packs organic protein into every serving.
